result.name: Delifrance - Central Two Chinachem Plaza

reviews.text: Breakfast is tasty. Convenient location. Not far away from Mid-Level Escalator.

Delifrance has some great afternoon tea packages! Do try their variety of croissants which they bake on the spot.
The staffs could be a bit more friendly. Lunch hours get busy so grab a table early if you are visiting for lunch.
Overpriced food court type pasta, only for those who wants to find a table to sit down for lunch instead in central
I realy don’t want act like Gorden Ramsey, but put a bit salt in the water before you cook pasta guys.
Very good food with good prices

result.name: DELIFRANCE - 中環華懋廣場二期

reviews.text: 近窗位置可下望電車路，边吃著碎蛋煙三文鱼治和喝著是日精選咖啡，边看著電車來回行走，真有人间何世的感覺！
不能稱之為法國餐廳，食物比一般茶餐廳精緻少少。
環境呀細啲但係食物不錯
